‘Into the Sun’, 2021, Alexander Zaxarov (zaxarov.com)

Ethereal is a lifelong and future-oriented NFT art project born at the intersection of the physical and the digital to immortalize the ethereal aspect of terrestrial life through digital photographs taken by Alexander Zaxarov around the world.
